txt.en: The invaders of Imping are numerous. Driving off even a fraction of their number will better position the Rohirrim to take back the village after you complete your mission within it.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Imping: The Miller's Foe to be underway in order to access Imping. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter Imping in order to complete this quest.</rgb>

The invaders of Imping are numerous. Driving off even a fraction of their number will better position the Rohirrim to take back the village after you complete your mission within it.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Imping: The Miller's Foe to be underway in order to access Imping. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter Imping in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
'You have done well, friend [placeholder]. Your efforts make our reclaimation of Imping even easier!'
To weaken the resolve of the invaders within Imping, you take it upon yourself to thin their numbers.
You should return to Ethelbryt and inform him of your deeds within Imping.
How fares your efforts in Imping? Should you lose your way, Gangfinda knows the paths to follow.
